Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ROMOS MARTIAL ARTS TOURNAMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the balloon!\NThe balloon has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has she been this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's brought more members.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona, as the princess\Nof a country, you must behave--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather the key figures\Nof our country at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is of the essence. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to wait for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest or train.\NJust prepare for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would somebody\Njust tell me what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us to Romos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Princess Leona\Nis leading the country to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You all haven't fully healed yet.\NRest comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and obey! I'm off to bed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for you to leave the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Test the results of your training here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ROMOS KINGDOM\NGRAND MARTIAL ARTS TOURNAMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not myself without this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes look clean, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru fixed them for me back in Teran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was so demure when we left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She took really good care of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she has a thing for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so dense when it comes to\Ngirls he's not interested in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a waste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mentor! Let's start my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With my powered-up spells,\NI'll blow away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So he finally managed to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll train later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually learned to cast\NRaiden by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I can do it any time\Nwithout the power of my crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. You've grown strong, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing compared\Nto his real power, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Now try using\Nthe power of your crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The power of the Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift from the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No weapon or armour can endure\Nthe full power of a Dragon Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but these clothes have been made with\Nspecial Papunican cloth and technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Knife of Papunica!\NI thought it burned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three Knives of Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one the princess had\Nand gave to you was the Sun Knife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one right here is the Wind Knife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the other one had a red gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's is green.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Knife has been lost,\Nso take care of this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use it when you're using\Nthe power of your crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Now try them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A perfect fit! You look good in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, the princess is currently\Nworking on something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she can't help in person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,she felt that giving you this equipment\Nwas the least she could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! The power of the crest\Neven lets him cast Toberura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great! It feels so light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Redemption Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dragonic Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He withstood it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done. Even my most powerful attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That scared me.\NHe suddenly fell out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought Dai's power of the crest\Nwas invincible, but it has a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of his Aura focused in his fist,\Nhis energy gets drained rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't control your energy use,\Nyou won't be able to fight long battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not its only weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fists will be enough\Nfor a normal enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but not against a powerful one like Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe if you had a sword\Nlike Baran's Demon Dragon Blade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Demon Dragon Blade really\Nthe only weapon a Dragon Knight can use?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's not true.\NThe world's a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are other\Namazing weapons out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nthe famous Sword of Champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Champions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Martial Arts Tournament in Romos...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Martial Arts Tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...the prize for the winner\Nis the Sword of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that true?! Is it?! Is it?!\N-Really?! Is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! Amy told me\Nwhen she came back from Romos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Champions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the prize for the tournament, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I met King Romos\Non orders from the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:08.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,ROMOS KINGDOM\NGRAND MARTIAL ARTS TOURNAMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to gather\Nstrong warriors to fight the Dark Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's holding a Martial Arts Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Any fighting style is allowed\Nas well as weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner will receive the legendary\NSword of Champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When's the tournament?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The preliminary fights begin at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Noon?! There's still time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At a Colosseum built\Na short distance from Romos Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can reach the castle with Rura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We should hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Martial Arts Tournament?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Straight down that road!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Down the path to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you!\N-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We just might make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's win this thing\Nand get the Sword of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. I thought they ran off in a hurry.\NSo they already went to Romos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably better than\Nwaiting around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Amy, what big thing\Nis Princess Leona planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not at liberty\Nto discuss that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But not only have\Nthe Papunica Troika been deployed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but the princess herself is traveling\Nthe world in preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, what are your plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'm hoping Baduck\Ncan repair my weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I apologize for this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To train?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle with Baran taught me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When powerful individuals\Nfight each other at full strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the battle becomes truly horrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a Dragonoid,\NBaran couldn't control his power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It turned him into a monster\Ncapable of killing his own son, Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to believe all I had to do\Nwas defeat my enemy, but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The power to fight and win isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've been given this Dark Armour\NSpear, I must live up to Larhart's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, I must gain the power\Nto stop even one like Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But how will you train?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have that much experience\Nwith a spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Book of Aban contains the secrets\Nof the Aban Style Spear Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So Aban was a master of the spear as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was a master\Nof all fighting styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I must master\Nthe Aban Style Spear Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and learn to use this Dark Armour Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Shouldn't you\Ntake the Book of Aban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need.\NI've read enough to memorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's a little too precious\Nfor me to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and Popp should have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Leave Dai and Papunica to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always so hard on himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's begun to realize his responsibility\Nas the eldest Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Dai will be able to win\Nthe Sword of Champions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This says...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The preliminary fights begin at noon,\Nbut registration ends an hour before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do something?!\NWe came all the way from Papunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a request from the Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But rules are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The preliminary fights are starting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who'll be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a crock.\NWhat did we waste all that effort for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we challenge the winner\Nand beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that what Heroes do?\N-What do you think?! Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, let's go home.\NForget the Sword of Champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we check out the tournament?\NWe might learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a domestic tournament in Romos.\NNo one interesting will be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hurry up!\NThere's a cute girl fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But we might just learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how cute she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not get to know\Nany girl this freakishly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three minutes, 15 seconds!\NThe Martial Artist Maam wins by knockout!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! That girl really is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next fight will begin in ten minutes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you entered this Martial Arts\NTournament as a Martial Artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! What a surprise!\NI didn't expect to run into you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it really Maam?\NI can't be sure. It could be a fake again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Maam's eyes should have\Na different look from Zaboera's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That slap's the real deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fat Rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem?!\NThe rules don't say a monster can't enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A talking Fat Rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line! You dare disrespect\NMiss Maam, you random pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Chiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about them.\NThis is Dai, Popp, and Gomechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is the Hero's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt, you little rat!\NI'm gonna roast you on a spit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my senior pupil. Please forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior pupil?! Ratty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was trained by Grand Master\NBrokin the Holy Fist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Karate Rat Chiu\Nwho studied together with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A Karate Rat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you're the Hero Dai\NI've heard so much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smaller than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next fight is between the\NWrestler Gomes and the Karate Rat Chiu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both fighters enter the ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit back and see my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Maam, I'll make quick work of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, pervert Mage!\NLet's talk later! Don't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. He's not a bad guy at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to be an evil monster\Nwho ravaged a local village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master Brokin captured him\Nand put him to training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He gained a strong heart immune\Nto the Dark Lord's evil will,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and studied to learn to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Brokin sounds impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we fought the Dragon Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh oh! We have to explain what happened\Ngently, or the shock might be a bit much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was such an ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp even died once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster wearing fighting gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know\Nmy real strength, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can defeat this thug\Nand show off how cool I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Maam's heart will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you need\Nthe Sword of Champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you win this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I win, I won't accept\Nthe Sword of Champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help you kill your own father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. This appears to be\Nquite a success, Mister Zamuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And it's all thanks to you,\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Gathering strong fighters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase our country's strength\Nwas your idea. I merely agreed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hope we gather many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our goal after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:48.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:53.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
